        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">About FarmConnect</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    FarmConnect is a platform designed to bridge the gap between farmers and buyers by simplifying the
                    contract farming process. Our goal is to empower farmers with secure, transparent contracts while
                    ensuring reliable market access for their produce.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 p-8 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
